Add extra utility to your rig with no drilling or bed modifications needed with the Access Adarac Truck Rack. Start by loosely bolting the included rails and spacer plates to the top of your truck's bed sides. Measure the distance in between the rails. Assembly the upright sections and crossbars and set to your measurement, but leave their bolt connections loose.
